Dear Shirley,
I’m sorry to hear that you are having difficulties with study and life. Maybe the following suggestions are helpful for you.

First of all, making a good learning plan can help you deal with the tasks. Besides, when you master a learning skill, it will be easy for you to finish homework. In this way, you will have more time to do what you like to do.

Second, why not have a communication with your friend after the fight? It is the best way to get on well with him (or her). And I do not think your friend will refuse to do that.

If you have anything questions, please write me at any time. And I am looking forward to hearing good news from you.
